{"tid":228420,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後連雪都未滑過，仲敢話自己好Sporty！","createTime":"2017-05-04T00:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T17:50:38.000Z","uid":19334,"like":10,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ccf9f2c043150e02b1a1998a2a74d7bf463a62e","tid":228420,"uid":19334,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:43:51.000Z","msg":"話說早兩日去做Interviewer，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁係間大型連鎖既零售公司，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都幾多人in既，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n儘管當中不乏90後，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但普遍黎講都係唔掂架啦，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁其中有一個更加有趣！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢自我介紹左3分鐘（其實無人會聽），<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我隱約聽到Sporty出現左成幾次，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 咁咪問下佢有幾Sporty，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢話自己識游水踩單車田徑三項鐵人...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我一句「識唔識滑雪？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢立即支吾以對！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁之後結果都不需要描述太多啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n估唔到依家d 90後連雪都未滑過就敢話自己Sporty！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c565658cb8fd00e31452d17b0a409257de5ae582","tid":228420,"uid":17607,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:47:19.000Z","msg":"On撚9"},{"pid":"1ba4a109e68c60a13ef3bc07d15d8c6f81f98a25","tid":228420,"uid":19334,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi